Over the weekend, Ukraine’s ambassador to South Africa, made an impassioned plea via social media. Responding also on social media, spokesperson for our department of international relations, Clayson Monyela, said the Ukrainian ambassador is not only wrong but also undiplomatic. Ambassador Liubov Abravitova spoke with eNCA's Sally Burdett. Courtesy of #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Ukraine’s ambassador to South Africa made an impassioned plea via social media. Liubov Abravitova said that the South African government has not reached out to her since the Russian invasion. READ: WATCH | Ukraine Ambassador to SA speaks on escalating conflict Dirco's Clayson  Monyela, responded, saying the Ukrainian ambassador is not only wrong but also undiplomatic. Abravitova says she is working on continuing the dialogue and collaboration between Ukraine and South Africa. Watch the video above for more details on this story.